VI editor
 vi filename
vim filename

i       - to insert into file
:wq     - to save file and quit
:q!       - to quit the file
dd    - to delete the line
shift + a  -- move cursor to end of the line
yy      - copies the current line
yw     - copies the current word
p    - to paste
u     - undo previously executed command

:1     - moves cursor to the start of the page
:$    - moves cursor to the end of the page

/keyword    to search for the particular keyword

:f filename    to rename a file will create as new file
